name: Imperial Artillery
Lore: 'The Empire always had a large weapons cache held in reserve, in case of an emergency.',
Text: 'During your control phase, if you have a weapon (except a lightsaber or [Permanent Weapon]) at a battleground you control, opponent loses 1 Force. OR If you just used a weapon (except a lightsaber or [Permanent Weapon]) to ''hit'' a character or starship, opponent loses 1 Force. (Immune to Sense.)',
